(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %)Jean(%%) __Baudrillard__(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %). “Art Between Utopia and Anticipation.” The Conspiracy of Art. 20(%%)__05__(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %). Page 90-92(%%).&#xD;
