) same deception(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %). There was a time - like in(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:6.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt&amp;#34; %)¶(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %) the film, The Purple Rose of Cairo - where(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:6.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %)¶(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt&amp;#34; %) the characters jumped off the screen(% style=&amp;#34;font-size: 6.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %)¶(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %) and entered into real life in order to be(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:6.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %)¶(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %) embodied - a poetic situational reversal.(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:6.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt&amp;#34; %)¶(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %) Today(% style=&amp;#34;font-size: 8pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12pt; background: lime; mso-highlight: lime&amp;#34; %), (% class=&amp;#34;StyleBoldUnderline&amp;#34; style=&amp;#34;background:lime;mso-highlight:lime&amp;#34; %)reality massively transfuses itself(% class=&amp;#34;StyleBoldUnderline&amp;#34; style=&amp;#34;font-size:6.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;background:lime;mso-highlight: lime&amp;#34; %)¶(% class=&amp;#34;StyleBoldUnderline&amp;#34; style=&amp;#34;background:lime;mso-highlight:lime&amp;#34; %) into the screen in order to become disembodied(% class=&amp;#34;StyleBoldUnderline&amp;#34; %).(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:6.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %)¶(%%) Nothing any longer separates(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:6.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %)¶(%%) them. The osmosis, the telemorphosis, is(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:6.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt&amp;#34; %)¶(%%) total.&#xD;
