(% class=&amp;#34;MsoNormal&amp;#34; %)&#xD;
**Schlag, 2002**(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) Pierre, Dheidt’s Real Father/BFF and Byron White Professor of Law, University of Colorado School of Law, “Commentary: The Aesthetics of American Law” 115 Harv. L. Rev. 1047&#xD;
&#xD;
(% class=&amp;#34;MsoNormal&amp;#34; %)&#xD;
(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) &#xD;
&#xD;
(% class=&amp;#34;MsoNormal&amp;#34; %)&#xD;
(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;background:yellow&amp;#34; %)__The perspectivist aesthetic has its own pathology. The attempt to see__(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt; font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %)or understand(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__everything from every place at once may__(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %), in the end,(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__yield no understanding at all__(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %)__. It’s a fine line between collage and total garbage. __(% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__The__(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %)crimped and(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__cramped gestures of some poststructuralist work__(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %), for example,(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__display the contortions that result from trying to avoid any foundationalist__(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %)or essentialist(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__moment — an attempt that is__(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %), in an important sense,(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__doomed to fail__(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %). Moreover,(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__the attempt to take in all perspectives can__(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %)__ simply __(% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__lead to indecision or paralysis__(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %).(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt; font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) Tout comprendre, c’est tout pardonner.(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__A contrary pathology is also common: the celebration of perspectivism may turn out to be merely a vehicle for the privileging of just one perspective__(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %)— namely,(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %) (% style=&amp;#34;font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family: ~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; background: yellow&amp;#34; %)__one’s own__(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;; mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %).&#xD;
