(% class=&amp;#34;FootnoteCharacters FootnoteCharacters&amp;#34; style=&amp;#34;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;;mso-fareast-font-family: ~&amp;#34;DejaVu Sans~&amp;#34;;mso-bidi-font-family:~&amp;#34;Lohit Hindi~&amp;#34;;mso-font-kerning:.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:HI;mso-bidi-language:HI&amp;#34; %)7url:#_ftnref7||name=&amp;#34;_ftn7&amp;#34;(%%)    (% class=&amp;#34;cite&amp;#34; style=&amp;#34;font-size: 12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt&amp;#34; %)Hannibal Lecter(%%),(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt&amp;#34; %) (The Silence of the Lambs, 1991)&#xD;
